32  CH112  MA121  PE101 2  ROTC  Foreign Language 102 First Semester  Second Year    Third Class Year EC201  BU210  BU220  Liberal Arts Elective  PE 200 11  ROTC  Foreign Language 201  Second Semester  Second  Year   Third Class Year EC202  EC203  BU230  Liberal Arts Elective  FMC take BU 314  PE 200 11  ROTC  Foreign Language 202  SE 300 First Semester  Third Year   Second Class Year EC300  EC304  3 Liberal Arts Electives  PE201  ROTC Second Semester  Third  Year   Second Class Year EC330  BU310  Liberal Arts Elective  BU Elective  FMC take Liberal Arts Elective  PE Elective  ROTC First Semester  Fourth Year   First Class Year   FMC   see note below under I  2 EC Electives  2 BU Electives  1 Free Elective  PE Elective  ROTC Second Semester  Fourth  Year   First Class Year BU440  2 EC Electives  1 BU Elective  1 Free Elective  PE Elective  ROTC For FMC only  Due to scheduling constraints  cadets electing FMC may 3 EC electives in the first semester and two BU electives in the second semester  Any cadet who wishes to take a course away from the Institute MUST HAVE THE TRANSFER APPROVAL COMPLETED BEFORE taking the class  ALL EC BU Core courses must be taken at VMI    Check Off List First Semester  First Year   RATS     EN 101      HI 103      CH 131      CH 111      MA 118      PE 101 2      ROTC      Foreign Language 101 Second Semester  First Year   RATS     EN 102     HI 104     CH 132     CH 112     MA 121     PE 101 2     ROTC     Foreign Language 102   First Semester  Second Year   Third Class Year     EC 201     BU 210     BU 220     Liberal Arts Elective     PE 200 11     ROTC     Foreign Language 201   Second Semester  Second  Year   Third Class Year     EC 202     EC 203     BU 230     Liberal Arts Elective  FMC take BU 314      PE 200 11     ROTC     Foreign Language 202  SE 300   First Semester  Third Year   Second Class Year     EC 300     EC 304     3 Liberal Arts Electives             PE 201     ROTC Second Semester  Third  Year   Second Class Year     